      <title>前大使称澳大利亚已为特朗普回归做好“充分准备”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/australia-well-prepared-for-trump-s-return-ex-ambassador-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前驻美国大使阿瑟·西诺迪诺斯表示，在澳大利亚努力与特朗普的盟友和支持者建立联系之后，澳大利亚为当选总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫做好了比 2016 年更好的准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/australia-well-prepared-for-trump-s-return-ex-ambassador-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 01:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普有望选择马尔科·卢比奥担任下一任国务卿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-expected-to-choose-marco-rubio-as-next-secretary-of-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士周一晚间表示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普预计将任命马尔科·卢比奥为国务卿，将他第二届政府的高位交给这位曾经的竞争对手，后者后来成为他在参议院最热心的支持者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-expected-to-choose-marco-rubio-as-next-secretary-of-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 01:58:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命的安全顾问视中国为“更大威胁”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-s-security-advisor-pick-sees-china-as-the-greater-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的国家安全顾问表示，美国应该努力结束欧洲和中东的冲突，以便能够应对来自中国的“更大威胁”，这表明未来几年超级大国之间的关系可能进一步紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-s-security-advisor-pick-sees-china-as-the-greater-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 01:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国计划削减购房税以刺激财政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-plans-to-slash-homebuying-taxes-in-fiscal-stimulus-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国政府正计划削减购房税，加大财政支持力度，以重振低迷的房地产市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/china-plans-to-slash-homebuying-taxes-in-fiscal-stimulus-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 01:46:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命退伍军人华尔兹担任国家安全顾问</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-picks-afghanistan-vet-waltz-as-national-security-advisor</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普选择佛罗里达州众议员迈克·沃尔兹担任国家安全顾问，将这位前陆军绿色贝雷帽和战斗老兵提拔为他最亲密的助手之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/trump-picks-afghanistan-vet-waltz-as-national-security-advisor</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 00:23:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普当选总统引发市场关注，美国国债收益率小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bond-investors-set-up-for-jump-in-yields-with-focus-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望重新点燃上周唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选后引发的抛售浪潮，美国国债开盘走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bond-investors-set-up-for-jump-in-yields-with-focus-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 20:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向国会盟友寻求内阁高级职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/trump-taps-miller-as-deputy-chief-as-immigration-takes-forefront</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普在扩充内阁时对众议院进行突击搜查，威胁在新政府成立初期削弱众议院议长迈克·约翰逊可能获得的微弱多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/trump-taps-miller-as-deputy-chief-as-immigration-takes-forefront</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 16:43:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党接近众议院多数席位和华盛顿三连胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/republicans-close-in-on-house-majority-and-a-washington-trifecta</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的领导下，众议院共和党人即将取得对华盛顿的统一控制，他们只需赢得众议院剩余 16 场未决竞选中的 4 场即可。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/republicans-close-in-on-house-majority-and-a-washington-trifecta</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 16:34:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列认为黎巴嫩停火谈判尽管存在障碍但仍取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/israel-sees-progress-in-lebanon-truce-talks-despite-hurdles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列称，在美国斡旋下，黎巴嫩停火的努力正在取得进展，但仍需要得到保证，如果真主党违反停火协议，以色列将恢复军事行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/israel-sees-progress-in-lebanon-truce-talks-despite-hurdles</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 15:00:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道，泰国将任命批评者为央行行长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/thailand-to-name-central-bank-critic-as-bot-chair-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国将任命前财政部长基迪拉特纳拉农 (Kittiratt Na-Ranong) 为新任泰国央行行长，这一迹象表明泰国政府试图加强对央行的控制，泰国央行与泰国政府在货币政策和通胀目标方面存在分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/thailand-to-name-central-bank-critic-as-bot-chair-reports-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 09:31:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
